room_title: Escape room "Hostage Rescue" by Lockdown Escape Rooms in Las Vegas
room_address: 3271 S Highland Dr, Las Vegas, NV 89109
room_description: The police have been investigating this kidnapping case for a while now. With the victim being your best friend, you can't idly sit on the sidelines anymore! The officer reveals that the kidnapper has set a deadline to cash in a million dollars. You have to find the account and wire the money before it's too late!
